		============================================= --> <section id="content"> <div class="content-wrap"> <div class="container clearfix"> <ol class="breadcrumb hidden-sm hidden-xs"> <li><img src="http://www.ripoffreport.com/assets/images/RORBullet.jpg" alt="-" class="mb2">&nbsp; <a href="/">Home</a> > Privacy Policy</li> </ol> <!-- Alerts Area --> <!-- End Alerts Area --> <section id="privacy-policy"> <div class="row"> <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12"> <ul class="leftNav"> <li><a href="/about-us">About Us</a></li> <li><a href="/consumers-say-thank-you/verified-safe">Ripoff Report Verified&trade;</a></li> <li><a href="/consumers-say-thank-you/ripoff-report-in-the-media">Ripoff Report in the Media</a></li> <li><a href="/consumers-say-thank-you/thank-you-letters">Thank You Letters</a></li> <li><a href="/consumers-say-thank-you/advertising-standards">Advertising Standards</a></li> <li><a href="/consumers-say-thank-you/advertising-with-us">Advertise With Us</a></li> <li><a href="/consumers-say-thank-you/want-to-sue-ripoff-report">Want to sue Ripoff Report?</a></li> <li><a href="/consumers-say-thank-you/false-report">There is a false report about me on Ripoff Report!</a></li> <li><a href="/consumers-say-thank-you/volunteer">Volunteer</a></li> <li><a href="/consumers-say-thank-you/donate">Donate</a></li> <li><a href="/consumers-say-thank-you/link-to-us">Link to Us</a></li> <li><a href="http://www.ripoffrevenge.com/" target="_blank">Revenge Guide</a></li> <li><a href="mailto:support@ripoffreport.com">Contact Us</a></li> <li><a href="/consumers-say-thank-you/terms-of-service">Terms of Service</a></li> </ul> </div> <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 middle"> <h1 class=pageTitle>Privacy Policy</h1> <p>This privacy policy applies to the Ripoff Report web site. Our contact information is:</p> <blockquote> <p>Ripoff Report<br>PO Box 310<br>Tempe AZ 85280 USA<br><a href="mailto:legal@ripoffreport.com">legal@ripoffreport.com</a></p> </blockquote> <p>We respect your privacy. This is why we have taken the time to disclose our information collection practices and our privacy policy. Please take the time to review this document.</p> <p>Collecting information provides specific benefits to our website visitors and by providing this information, our staff can contact you regarding your report for verification or follow-up if necessary.</p> <p>We collect information for the following purpose(s):</p> <ul> <li>Verifying reports
				<li>Website and system administration
				<li>Research and development
				<li>Preserving social history as governed by existing law or policy
				<li>Users filing a Ripoff Report or rebuttal may opt-in if they would be willing to be contacted by the media, a consumer advocate, lawyer, or government authority to help further their cause or to help with an investigation against the business or individual </li></ul> <p>Who has access to the information we collect?</p> <ul> <li>Ourselves - Unless you opt-in as mentioned above, information is only shared with the operators of this website. </li> </ul> <p>Of the information we do collect, we do not provide our visitors with access to information we collect.</p> <p>If you believe that our website has collected incorrect information or if you would like to dispute any information, please contact us using the address at the top of this page.</p> <h2>Privacy Policy</h2> <p></p> <p>Protecting your private information
				is our priority.  This Statement of Privacy applies to the <a href="http://www.ripoffreport.com" target="_blank">www.ripoffreport.com</a>
				and governs data collection and usage of such data. For the purposes
				of this Privacy Policy, unless otherwise noted, all references to Ripoff
				Report includes <a href="http://www.ripoffreport.com" target="_blank">www.ripoffreport.com</a>.  By using the Ripoff Report website, you consent to the data
				practices described in this statement.</p> <p></p> <p style="font-weight:bold">Collection of your Personal Information</p> <p>Ripoff Report may collect personally identifiable
				information, including but not limited to, your name, address, phone
				number, and e-mail address.  If you purchase Ripoff Report&#39;s products
				and services, we may in connection with those products and services,
				create a publicly visible profile that includes your name/company name
				and photographs.  In addition we will collect billing and credit
				card information.  This information is used to complete the purchase
				transaction. Ripoff Report may also collect anonymous demographic information,
				which is not unique to you, such as your age and gender. We may gather
				additional personal or non-personal information in the future.  </p> <p></p> <p>Information about your computer/device hardware and
				software may be automatically collected by Ripoff Report. This information
				can include: your IP address, browser type, domain names, access times
				and referring website addresses. This information is used for the operation
				of the service, to maintain quality of the service, and to provide general
				statistics regarding use of the Ripoff Report website.  </p> <p></p> <p>Please keep in mind that if you directly disclose
				personally identifiable information or personally sensitive data through
				Ripoff Report&#39;s public message boards, this information may be collected
				and used by others.  </p> <p></p> <p>Ripoff Report encourages you to review the privacy
				statements of websites you choose to link to from Ripoff Report so that
				you can understand how those websites collect, use and share your information.
				Ripoff Report is not responsible for the privacy statements or other
				content on websites outside of the Ripoff Report website.  </p> <p></p> <p style="font-weight:bold">Use of your Personal Information </p> <p>Ripoff Report collects and uses your personal information
				to provide, maintain, protect and improve upon its products, services,
				and the operation of its website.  This includes, but is not limited
				to, keeping records of your communication with Ripoff Report and using
				your e-mail address to inform you about upcoming changes or improvements
				to our services or that of our affiliates.  </p> <p></p> <p>Ripoff Report may also use your personally identifiable
				information to inform you of other products or services available from
				Ripoff Report and its affiliates. Ripoff Report may also contact you
				via e-mail or other through other modes of communication with surveys
				to conduct research about your opinion of current services or of potential
				new services that may be offered.  </p> <p></p> <p>Ripoff Report may, from time to time, contact you
				on behalf of external business partners about a particular offering
				that may be of interest to you. In those cases, your unique personally
				identifiable information (e-mail, name, address, telephone number) is
				transferred to the third party.  Ripoff Report may share data with
				trusted partners to help perform statistical analysis, send you email
				or postal mail, provide customer support, or arrange for deliveries.
				All such third parties are prohibited from using your personal information
				except to provide these services to Ripoff Report, and they are required
				to maintain the confidentiality of your information.  </p> <p></p> <p>Ripoff Report may keep track of the websites and
				pages our users visit within Ripoff Report, in order to determine what
				Ripoff Report services are the most popular. This data is used to deliver
				customized content and advertising within Ripoff Report to customers
				whose behavior indicates that they are interested in a particular subject
				area.  </p> <p></p> <p>Ripoff Report will disclose your personal information,
				without notice, only if required to do so by law or in the good faith
				belief that such action is necessary to: (a) conform to the edicts of
				the law or comply with legal process served on Ripoff Report or the
				site; (b) protect and defend the rights or property of Ripoff Report;
				and, (c) act under exigent circumstances to protect the personal safety
				of users of Ripoff Report, or the public.  </p> <p></p> <p style="font-weight:bold">Use of Cookies</p> <p>The Ripoff Report website may use &quot;cookies&quot;
				and other technologies to help you personalize your online experience.
				A cookie is a text file that is placed on your hard disk by a web page
				server. Cookies cannot be used to run programs or deliver viruses to
				your computer. Cookies are uniquely assigned to you, and can only be
				read by a web server in the domain that issued the cookie to you.  </p> <p> </p> <p>One of the primary purposes
				of cookies is to provide a convenience feature to save you time. The
				purpose of a cookie is to tell the web server that you have returned
				to a specific page. For example, if you personalize Ripoff Report pages,
				or register with Ripoff Report site or services, a cookie helps Ripoff
				Report to recall your specific information on subsequent visits. This
				simplifies the process of recording your personal information, such
				as billing addresses, shipping addresses, and so on. When you return
				to the same Ripoff Report website, the information you previously provided
				can be retrieved, so you can easily use the Ripoff Report features that
				you customized.  </p> <p></p> <p>You have the ability to accept or decline cookies.
				Most web browsers automatically accept cookies, but you can usually
				modify your browser setting to decline cookies if you prefer. If you
				choose to decline cookies, you may not be able to fully experience the
				interactive features of the Ripoff Report services or websites you visit.
			</p> <p></p> <p style="font-weight:bold">Security of your Personal Information</p> <p>Ripoff Report secures your personal information from
				unauthorized access, use or disclosure. When personal information (such
				as a credit card number) is transmitted to other websites, it is protected
				through the use of encryption, such as the Secure Sockets Layer (SSL)
				protocol.  </p> <p></p> <p style="font-weight:bold">Children Under Thirteen</p> <p>Ripoff Report does not knowingly collect personally
				identifiable information from children under the age of thirteen. If
